tags: $Script

# Tests (positive)
* `<<foo.hello John Smith>>`: <<foo.hello John Smith>>
* `<<foo.test 1 true "Car Wash">>`: <<foo.test 1 true "Car Wash">>
* `<<foo.object name:"John Smith" age:22>>`: <<foo.object name:"John Smith" age:22>>
* `<<foo.object {"name":"John Smith", "age":"22"}>>`: <<foo.object {"name":"John Smith", "age":"22"}>>
* `<<foo.test ${1+1} true "1+1=2">>`: <<foo.test ${1+1} true "1 + 1 = 2">>
* `<<foo.test "${1 + 1}" true "1 + 1 = 2">>`: <<foo.test "${1 + 1}" true "1 + 1 = 2">>

# Tests (which should fail)
* `<<foo.object {"name":"John Smith", age:22}>>`: <<foo.object {"name":"John Smith", age:22}>>

# Code
```javascript
tw.extensions.registerMacro('foo', 'hello', (firstName, lastName) => {
  return `Hello ${firstName + ' ' + lastName}`;
}, {version: '1.0.0'});

tw.extensions.registerMacro('foo', 'test', (age, boolean, string) => {
  return `Age: ${age} (${typeof age}), Boolean: ${boolean} (${typeof boolean}), String: ${string} (${typeof string})`;
}, {version: '1.0.0'});

tw.extensions.registerMacro('foo', 'object', ({name, age}) => {
  return `Age: ${age + 1} (${typeof age}), Name: ${name} (${typeof name})`;
}, {version: '1.0.0'});
```